title: Ubehage's MegaStress Tool
description:
Ubehage's MegaStress Tool
-------------------------

This is a small tool, that will put your computer under a significant amount of stress!

When you run this application, it will launch millions upon millions of threads, as well as consuming exabytes of memory.
Of course, there is a warning for you. You cannot run this by mistake.


No damage will be done, but you will propably not be able to shut down Windows normally.
